11️⃣ Summary / Best Practices for SREs

Know both SQL and NoSQL basics.

Automate backup, restore, replication, and monitoring.

Monitor key metrics: latency, throughput, replication lag, disk/memory usage.

Understand high availability, failover, and scaling strategies.

Document and script operations for reproducibility.

Always test recovery procedures in a lab.
